    ('SPEA-V 380', 'INTERNSHIP IN PUBLIC AND ENVIRONMENTAL AFFAIRS', '3009', 'Class Status', NULL, NULL, 'Brian Seavey', 145, NULL, 'Independent Study', '6', NULL, ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Students and faculty must complete appropriate paperwork prior to or during experience. Retroactive experiential credit will not be awarded. Students work with public agencies or governmental units for assignment to a defined task relevant to their educational interests in public affairs. Tasks may involve staff work or research.', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], NULL),
